    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable ride that\u2019s ready for the daily grind? This car is a solid runner with plenty of life left! While it shows some honest wear and tear from its years of service, it remains a reliable choice for anyone seeking practical transportation. It\u2019s got a great engine, a functional interior, and that classic charm you can only get from a car that's been well-loved and used. Perfect for a first car or a trusty commuter!",
