    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The exterior shows minor signs of regular use, such as small stone chips, but the paint remains glossy and free of major dents. Inside, the cabin is clean with minimal wear on the upholstery, and all electronics, including the infotainment and climate control, are fully functional. Mechanically, the car runs smoothly with a consistent service history, though it will eventually need standard preventative maintenance like new brake pads in the coming year. It\u2019s a reliable, solid choice for anyone looking for a dependable daily driver that has been treated with care.",
