    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in exemplary, showroom-preserved condition, this vehicle represents the definitive standard for its model. Every facet, from the lustrous, original paintwork to the impeccable interior surfaces, reflects a history of uncompromising stewardship. Mechanically superior and visually indistinguishable from its initial delivery state, this unit offers a rare opportunity for the sophisticated collector who demands absolute perfection. This is not merely a pre-owned vehicle; it is a meticulously maintained asset of the highest order.",
      "price": 48900.0,
