    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector\u2019s dream, maintained with obsessive care to preserve its showroom-fresh state. The exterior paint retains its deep, glass-like luster, free from any swirls, chips, or road imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in an untouched state; the premium leather upholstery is supple and shows zero signs of wear, while the original floor mats look as though they have never seen a shoe. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It has been strictly garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and has followed a rigorous maintenance schedule with every service performed at the authorized dealership. From the crisp response of the engine to the silent, smooth operation of every interior switch and dial, this car provides a driving experience identical to the day it rolled off the assembly line. It comes complete with all original keys, manuals, and a comprehensive folder of service records. This is a rare opportunity to own a flawless example of automotive excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
